@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_chrksf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp(0.48))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.57) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.88)) - 0.94)
    tmp = (tmp - wp.sin(tmp))
    v2 = (0.26 / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.96) * 0.26))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp(0.09))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v2 + 0.78 - v2 + 0.83)))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.93) - (v2 + 0.29 * v0 + 0.68)) - wp.abs((v0 + 0.20 * v1 + 0.72)))
    data[tid] = v0
